Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.80,0:14:50.39,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}「長大成人了啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.56,0:14:54.67,songjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ちょっと油断してる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.56,0:14:54.67,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}有些大意了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.43,0:14:57.89,songjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}キミの横顔をね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.43,0:14:57.89,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你的側臉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.24,0:15:01.91,songjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}みているのよ　まだ今でも
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.24,0:15:01.91,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我一直在看著哦
